title: Her Parents Are Kicking Her Out To Make Room For WHAT?!
description:
Our intern Mackenzie goes to college near home. Because of this, she often goes home during the weekends. However, her parents are running out of space and need to make room for her dad's office ASAP!
Their plan is to turn her room into his new office, that means kicking her out. How does she feel about this? She explains...
